  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a wok over high heat, until it starts to smoke.",
    "Add the chopped onion and minced garlic, stir-fry until they start to caramelize.",
    "Add the diced sweet potato and grated carrot, stir-fry for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the peanuts and cayenne pepper, stir-fry for another 2 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a serving plate, garnish with chopped fresh parsley.",
    "Serve immediately, while the wok-hei is still present."
